We ran a 3mnth experiment in 2017 where we served 700 clients for free. In most cases affirmation & guides were enough to help. Where legal intervention was needed, AI reduced the cost by 60%. We have no doubt that legaltech can greatly improve access to justice. #futureoflaw #ai
